Each Person, Couple and Family is Unique!

What are the different types of psychologists and what exactly do they do in the variety of branches of psychology? When people hear the term psychologist, many immediately imagine a person sitting in an office, scribbling notes while a client sits on a leather fainting couch. Sure, there are plenty of psychologists who engage in this type of talk therapy.
